item.title: CVE-2020-1855|2024-08-04T06:53:58.916Z -- huawei -- hege-570
item.description: Huawei HEGE-570 version 1.0.1.22(SP3); and HEGE-560, OSCA-550, OSCA-550A, OSCA-550AX, and OSCA-550X version 1.0.1.21(SP3) have an insufficient verification vulnerability. An attacker can access the device physically and exploit this vulnerability to tamper with device information. Successful exploit may cause service abnormal.
